## âœ… GitHub Actions

A simple CI workflow to check if the React frontend builds successfully on every push to `main`.

ğŸ“ Located in:
```
.github/workflows/build.yml
```

Action Steps:
- Checks out code
- Installs frontend dependencies
- Runs `npm run build`

âœ… Pass = React app builds successfully

